#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "thig3.6:3.1"
msgid "6. Sukkātherīgāthā"
msgstr ""

#. </h1></div><blockquote class="gatha"><p><a class="sc" id="1"></a><a
#. class="verse-num-sc" id="verse-num-sc54"></a><a class="verse-num-pts"
#. id="verse-num-pts54"></a>
msgctxt "thig3.6:4.1"
msgid "“<span class=\"var\" title=\"kime (bj)\" id=\"note25\">Kiṃme</span> katā rājagahe manussā,"
msgstr "What’s up with these people in Rājagaha?"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thig3.6:4.2"
msgid "<span class=\"var\" title=\"madhupītāva (bj) | madhuṃ pītā (pts1-2)\" id=\"note26\">Madhuṃ pītāva</span> acchare;"
msgstr "They sleep like they’ve been drinking mead!"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thig3.6:4.3"
msgid "Ye sukkaṃ na upāsanti,"
msgstr "They don’t attend on Sukkā"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thig3.6:4.4"
msgid "Desentiṃ buddhasāsanaṃ."
msgstr "as she’s teaching the Buddha’s instructions. "

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="2"></a><a class="verse-num-sc"
#. id="verse-num-sc55"></a><a class="verse-num-pts" id="verse-num-pts55"></a>
msgctxt "thig3.6:5.1"
msgid "Tañca appaṭivānīyaṃ,"
msgstr "But the wise—"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thig3.6:5.2"
msgid "asecanakamojavaṃ;"
msgstr "it’s as if they drink it up,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thig3.6:5.3"
msgid "Pivanti maññe sappaññā,"
msgstr "so irresistible, delicious and nutritious,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thig3.6:5.4"
msgid "valāhakamivaddhagū."
msgstr "like travelers enjoying a cool cloud.”"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="3"></a><a class="verse-num-sc"
#. id="verse-num-sc56"></a><a class="verse-num-pts" id="verse-num-pts56"></a>
msgctxt "thig3.6:6.1"
msgid "Sukkā sukkehi dhammehi,"
msgstr "“You’re Sukkā because of your bright qualities"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thig3.6:6.2"
msgid "vītarāgā samāhitā;"
msgstr "Desireless, with unified mind"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thig3.6:6.3"
msgid "Dhāreti antimaṃ dehaṃ,"
msgstr "Bearing your final body"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thig3.6:6.4"
msgid "jetvā māraṃ savāhinin”ti."
msgstr "Having conquered Māra and his army”"

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsutta"><a class="sc" id="4"></a>
